sessiondvd
Class StandardSession

java.lang.Object
  sessiondvd.StandardSession
All Implemented Interfaces:
sSession
Direct Known Subclasses:
AdminSession
 class StandardSession
extends java.lang.Object
implements sSession

This class contains all functionality that is command between ADMIN and STANDARD sessions. This includes, buying, renting, returning, creating Transaction File, reading Current DVD File and etc.

Author:
100413064 (Shivam Kalra), 100400174 (Nishant Bhatt)

_buy

protected void _buy(java.lang.String title,
                    int quantity,
                    boolean limit_check)
This is protected method that is called with different parameters from inherited class. As per the requirement specification, ADMIN can buy any numbers of DVD(s), therefore, variable limit_check must be false when method is called from ADMIN session.

Parameters:
title - DVDs title
quantity - Number of DVD(s) for a particular title.
limit_check - If there is restriction of number of DVD(s) to buy.
